The '''Chinese Cycling Association''' (in [[Simplified Chinese]]: 中国自行车运动协会) is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[China]]..

It is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Asian Cycling Confederation]].

