'''Coxen Hole Stadium''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Coxen Hole]], [[Roatan]], [[Honduras]].  It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of [[Arsenal FC (Roatan)|Arsenal FC]].  The stadium holds 2,000 people.

