{{Infobox stadium | image = |stadium_name = Joypurhat Stadium | opened = | location = [[Joypurhat]], [[Bangladesh]] | owner = [[National Sports Council]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nsc.gov.bd/category/structure/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2013-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912054054/http://nsc.gov.bd/category/structure/ |archivedate=2013-09-12 |df= }}</ref> | operator = [[National Sports Council]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nsc.gov.bd/category/structure/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2013-09-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912054054/http://nsc.gov.bd/category/structure/ |archivedate=2013-09-12 |df= }}</ref> | surface = [[Grass]] | seating_capacity = 1000+ | tenants = Joypurhat Football Team }} '''Joypurhat Stadium''' is situated at Master Para, [[Joypurhat]], [[Bangladesh]].
